{"legal_anchor": "Art. 9(2)(b), Reg. 2024/1689", "clause": "The risk management system shall comprise... estimation and evaluation of the risks that may emerge when the high-risk AI system is used in accordance with its intended purpose, and the possible reasonably foreseeable misuse.", "violation_subtlety": "borderline", "uncertainty_factor": 0.4, "compliance_justification": "Failing to evaluate and mitigate the risk of adversarial inputs (a form of reasonably foreseeable misuse) violates the risk management process mandated by Article 9(2)(b).", "compliant_fix": "@app.post("/content-moderate")
