{"legal_anchor": "Art. 12(2), Reg. 2024/1689", "clause": "The logs shall be kept for a period that is appropriate in view of the intended purpose of the high-risk AI system and applicable legal obligations.", "violation_subtlety": "borderline", "uncertainty_factor": 0.4, "compliance_justification": "The snippet explicitly caps retention at seven days while using an unstructured local file without access control or linkage to a documented retention assessment. For many high-risk systems that horizon is unlikely to satisfy 'appropriate' retention for audit, safety monitoring, or legal holds.", "compliant_fix": "def log_inference(input_data, output):
