{"legal_anchor": "Art. 13(3), Reg. 2024/1689", "clause": "High-risk AI systems shall be accompanied by instructions for use that include concise, complete, correct and clear information that is relevant, accessible and comprehensible to deployers.", "violation_subtlety": "borderline", "uncertainty_factor": 0.45, "compliance_justification": "Instructions for use must be 'concise, complete, correct and clear information that is... comprehensible to deployers.' Providing a full research paper fails the conciseness and comprehensibility requirements for operational deployers who are not AI researchers.", "compliant_fix": "@app.get("/instructions")
